{"tid":140131,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"500 days of summer VS La La Land","createTime":"2017-03-02T03:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T18:14:37.000Z","uid":32051,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"297a8515eb52599e880848651726bb5b1440afeb","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"兩套戲兩位同樣大受美國女人/<span style=\"color: red;\">港女</span>歡迎，同樣有代入感的角色。<br />\n<br />\n對男人而言，同樣是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span>，兩者之間，大家覺得邊位更賤？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://bee.newmonday.com.hk/blog/oceanchan/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/blog_00011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbee.newmonday.com.hk%2Fblog%2Foceanchan%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2010%2F02%2Fblog_00011.jpg&h=9fbf72bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n500 days of Summer由mv導演拍攝。<br />\n（以下為電影發行商給予yahoo的簡介）故事圍繞一對輾轉相識500天的俊男美女，男愛女，女不愛男，戀人關係的發展限於約會上床鬧翻分手，這些指定動作從打亂的時序呈現，解讀出層出不窮戀愛新定義。第488天先來預告 ，阿心（素兒狄絲查露） 已戴上結婚戒指；倒回第1 天，阿湯（祖瑟夫哥頓利域）一見認定她是夢中情人，每分每秒為她心跳；然而到第一次約會，她已示警自己不相信愛情。阿湯的愛情觀超浪漫，阿心和男人超快親熱，每段戲都緊貼時代愛情脈膊。這不是愛情故事，而是詮釋愛情、解構愛情的窩心絮語&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> for Summer<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.upanh123.com/2016/12/22/cover02c11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.upanh123.com%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2Fcover02c11.jpg&h=37ab0d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLa La Land由奧斯卡最年輕得獎導演拍攝。<br />\n（以下為電影發行商給予yahoo的簡介）<br />\n薩巴斯安(賴恩高斯寧 飾)與美亞(愛瑪史東 飾)在洛杉磯繁囂都市中相遇，紛擾擠塞的高速公路正正是他們處於人生樽頸位的寫照。在這個星夢之城，二人卻在追求著無法達成的夢：爵士樂手薩巴斯安想在21世紀喚醒人們對傳統爵士樂的關注；夢想成為演員的美亞只是希望能夠成功完成一次試鏡。迷失星途的他們沒想到這次邂逅，會牽引著彼此向夢想躍進一大步，走向聲色光影的璀璨世界。他們尋找快樂，但同時也要面對熱情與夢想帶來的痛......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> for Mia"},{"pid":"df0861558ac92fce8cb690f00f2999a8025ec198","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"Summer罪行: 交往時，自稱不相信愛情、婚姻，唔打算負責唔諗住認真，自稱唔係同男主角拍拖但繼續拍拖生活。覺得看不透與男主角將來飛甩佢，然後半年後嫁作人婦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMia罪行：<span style=\"color: purple;\">葡萄</span>男主角事業有成，追夢成名後，嫁完人生埋"},{"pid":"c70002f5f14538cef4de902860a90db9b9d86676","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f1f6d22c589726430454a06c242fb0cef2c420ee","tid":140131,"uid":83682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"好難揀喎"},{"pid":"8b8d453e6fb1c7d93cf69a1503ae82a7be943c24","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難揀喎</blockquote><br />\n臭雞界 一時瑜亮"},{"pid":"1aebf4f65411a21d747145f9cab3344e535f7a3b","tid":140131,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"about time贏呢兩套九條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eea550516fede33b7b225dc40fbedbb0cb160c","tid":140131,"uid":84518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"La La Land, opps...Moonlight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a59825553ca886c60e1d12e88e3b0c9cbae4679","tid":140131,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>about time贏呢兩套九條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nabout time 個一個都算係臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1886e28a066676b757176ec1fa3b0bcb295196d9","tid":140131,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"Summer 死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54801dce0a7c8648d5a8fca1e14342f85fada9d5","tid":140131,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"女人反轉豬肚就係屎<br />\n今日話好愛你<br />\n聽日就可以分手<br />\n當中唔需要有一個合理既原因<br />\n只係一下有感覺要分手就會分手<br />\n就算離婚都係咁係唔需要理由<br />\n<br />\n男人追女成功贏既係女人既感覺<br />\n男入比女飛輸既都係女人既感覺<br />\n唔好以為你贏到係佢既芳心"},{"pid":"eb984ccb4e3cd25bf69b21ea264f8203a5043e85","tid":140131,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"500 days of summer 影響我好大，好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd81ea712b5d02911d7691771c269ce9a6fb088","tid":140131,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>about time贏呢兩套九條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夠晒cheesy"},{"pid":"2a678ce46f742071a3768e1b6346dff1af2f80a6","tid":140131,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"500days of summer係比男人睇架"},{"pid":"1eb20345a26ec681e827905e56d0d07b4e09b9f7","tid":140131,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:12:35.000Z","msg":"正皮 for sure, 500 days of summer 好睇好多"},{"pid":"9893ef8e277bf64d9295ad306b809a2b8b768023","tid":140131,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500days of summer係比男人睇架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有道理"},{"pid":"a6745c299e4569cd1b1486e12dd052b914122f0c","tid":140131,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"500都睇到我火都黎，竟然有人話好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b7c95729a32931a8ce27789c9543f3ed39dac0","tid":140131,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500都睇到我火都黎，竟然有人話好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係睇撚到火先正 睇完之後係其他電影見到Zooey Deschanel都會自動覺得佢個角色係 bitch"},{"pid":"bec9ad74085ef1c402af595afed11d8d6658a6b2","tid":140131,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500都睇到我火都黎，竟然有人話好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇係因為講得中<br />\n男人代入到Tom嘅角色係因為大部分男人都長唔大，活喺自己comfort zone 裡面，有夢想亦有相應嘅才能，但就安於踎喺一個發揮唔到嘅位置上浪費青春同才能<br />\n<br />\n覺得Summer係bitch係臭雞嘅，只係唔願意面對Tom同Summer之間嘅價值觀真係好唔同，縱然Summer係閃電結婚，但最後佢終於認同Tom世界上真係有美好愛情，我認為去到嗰個位，Tom都理應釋懷了，至少佢都有D影響到Summer"},{"pid":"94e20575ffbe52050d4c591dfc478b374df74706","tid":140131,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"一套愛情小品<br />\n一套歌舞<br />\n好難比喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋lala land 根本唔係劇情出眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afd3dd1ca073cb16504534cfb560ec11d255b7c","tid":140131,"uid":34805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"係咪我問題<br />\n唔係比緊summer同mia咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5d329cf8a1467651e434bdfa1a6b5dc1f3d8e9","tid":140131,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪我問題<br />\n唔係比緊summer同mia咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但樓主個topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f079623a219dab23be1df19540b43650d91121fc","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T00:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>500都睇到我火都黎，竟然有人話好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇係因為講得中<br />\n男人代入到Tom嘅角色係因為大部分男人都長唔大，活喺自己comfort zone 裡面，有夢想亦有相應嘅才能，但就安於踎喺一個發揮唔到嘅位置上浪費青春同才能<br />\n<br />\n覺得Summer係bitch係臭雞嘅，只係唔願意面對Tom同Summer之間嘅價值觀真係好唔同，縱然Summer係閃電結婚，但最後佢終於認同Tom世界上真係有美好愛情，我認為去到嗰個位，Tom都理應釋懷了，至少佢都有D影響到Summer</blockquote><br />\n理解佢地之間既問題，唔等於summer唔係一個自私的賤人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83be36700bf3b33e8c8e62fd8096185f8de1d36e","tid":140131,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T00:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪我問題<br />\n唔係比緊summer同mia咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但樓主個topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n變左邊套好睇我topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令人誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3453725c5383ed098151cf6b7d14e648e1e10598","tid":140131,"uid":83682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500 days of summer 影響我好大，好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1911c22be17daa3f31b2156958cf4f5bf73f71","tid":140131,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>500都睇到我火都黎，竟然有人話好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇係因為講得中<br />\n男人代入到Tom嘅角色係因為大部分男人都長唔大，活喺自己comfort zone 裡面，有夢想亦有相應嘅才能，但就安於踎喺一個發揮唔到嘅位置上浪費青春同才能<br />\n<br />\n覺得Summer係bitch係臭雞嘅，只係唔願意面對Tom同Summer之間嘅價值觀真係好唔同，縱然Summer係閃電結婚，但最後佢終於認同Tom世界上真係有美好愛情，我認為去到嗰個位，Tom都理應釋懷了，至少佢都有D影響到Summer</blockquote><br />\n理解佢地之間既問題，唔等於summer唔係一個自私的賤人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但Summer賤唔賤並冇影響套戲好唔好睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔多覺得Summer真係有你地講到咁賤，有D位都係Tom一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n不過我認同Summer有玩弄感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}